Feed an average size adult cat 1 can per 3 to 3 1/2 lbs of body weight daily. Feed up to twice this amount to **kittens**. **Pregnant or nursing cats** may require two to four times their normal feeding.

When introducing a pet to a new food, we recommend a gradual change over a 10 day period. Start by feeding 90% of their old food and 10% of Fancy Feast. Each day, increase their portion of Fancy Feast by 10%, while decreasing their old food until 100% of their meal consists of their new food.

keyBenefits: This grain-free cat food is made without artificial colors or preservatives.
Crafted with real, high-quality ingredients to deliver a 100% complete and balanced meal for adult cats.
Developed in partnership with Purina's pet nutritionists to create an unforgettable experience for your cat.
Made with real cod, sole and shrimp; savory salmon; or ocean whitefish and tuna as the number one ingredient with a smooth pate texture.
These protein-rich, gourmet Purina pate recipes create a flavor-filled experience with savory cat food gravy to add to the delicious taste.

itemSubHeader.richText: From smooth pates to rich gravies and delicate broths, Fancy Feast lovingly crafts an array of mouthwatering wet foods for your cat. Pamper your kitty with delicious tastes and textures designed to delight with every exquisite detail.
Deliciously smooth, finely ground pates offer a taste and texture cats love.
Each recipe is carefully crafted with real, high-quality meat, poultry or seafood.
These Fancy Feast recipes provide 100% complete and balanced nutrition for adult cats.
Fancy Feast meals are crafted in US facilities, for your peace of mind and your cat’s total satisfaction.

As a gourmet cat food brand loved by cats worldwide, Fancy Feast is known for creating unique taste experiences that delight cats again and again. With more than 100 irresistible recipes ranging from smooth pates and tender bites to gourmet gravies and delicate broths, there’s a plate to please any palate. Fancy Feast has been making cat food with love since 1982, crafting the delicious tastes and irresistible textures that cats crave for over 30 years.
